---
import Handbook from "../layouts/Handbook.astro";
---
<Handbook title="Emergency" current="emergency">
  <h1>Emergency</h1>
  <section class="panel">
    <h2>立即撥打</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1.4rem;font-family:var(--font-display)">112 警察 · 119 消防／醫療</p>
  </section>
  <section class="panel">
    <h2>官方</h2>
    <p><a href="https://www.roc-taiwan.org/kr" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">駐韓國台北代表部</a>（出發前重查電話）</p>
    <p class="muted">保險緊急電話：REPLACE_ME（離線保存）</p>
  </section>
  <section class="panel">
    <h2>住宿（占位）</h2>
    <p>首爾韓文地址：REPLACE_ME</p>
    <p>釜山韓文地址：REPLACE_ME</p>
    <p>對計程車說：이 주소로 가 주세요</p>
  </section>
  <section class="panel">
    <h2>飲食／求助</h2>
    <p>저희는 술을 마시지 않아요</p>
    <p>갑각류 해산은 빼 주실 수 있나요?</p>
    <p>도와주세요</p>
    <p>구급차를 불러 주세요</p>
  </section>
  <p class="muted">完整離線版見 dist/emergency-pack.pdf</p>
</Handbook>
